For hooks that _do_ pertain to the particular visited file, use
`«c:write-file-functions»'.  Both this variable and
`«c:write-file-functions»' relate to how a buffer is saved to file.
To perform various checks or updates before the buffer is saved,
use `«c:before-save-hook»'."»)
