(«k:defun» «f:locate-user-emacs-file» (new-name «t:&optional» old-name)
  «d:"Return an absolute per-user Emacs-specific file name.
If NEW-NAME exists in `«c:user-emacs-directory»', return it.
Else if OLD-NAME is non-nil and ~/OLD-NAME exists, return ~/OLD-NAME.
