More precisely, use this coding system in place of the
value of `«c:buffer-file-coding-system»', when saving the buffer.
Calling `«c:write-region»' for any purpose other than saving the buffer
will still use `«c:buffer-file-coding-system»'; this variable has no effect
in such cases."»)

